      • getType

        public String getType()

        The specific kind of item. Possible values are:

        • Armor
        • Bag
        • Consumable
        • Container
        • CraftingMaterial
        • Gizmo
        • MiniPet
        • Trinket
        • Trophy
        • UpgradeComponent
        • Weapon

        Each of these types is represented by it's on POJO that is an implementation of Item. Each POJO is named in the format TypeItem. For example, an "Armor" item is represented by the ArmorItem object.

        Specified by:
        getType in interface Item
        Returns:
